  45:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****                   __HAL_USART_ENABLE_IT() and __HAL_USART_DISABLE_IT() inside the transmit and rece
  46:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****           (++) DMA Configuration if you need to use DMA process (HAL_USART_Transmit_DMA()
  47:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****                HAL_USART_Receive_DMA() and HAL_USART_TransmitReceive_DMA() APIs):
