  53:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****             (+++) Configure the priority and enable the NVIC for the transfer
  54:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****                   complete interrupt on the DMA Tx/Rx channel.
