 231:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****       (+) For the synchronous SPI mode only these parameters can be configured:
 232:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) Baud Rate
 233:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) Word Length
 234:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) Stop Bit
 235:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) Parity: If the parity is enabled, then the MSB bit of the data written
 236:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****              in the data register is transmitted but is changed by the parity bit.
 237:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) USART polarity
 238:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) USART phase
 239:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) USART LastBit
 240:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) Receiver/transmitter modes
