 264:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****     |    1    |    0    |    0      |    | SB |    7 bit data   | STB |     |
 265:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****     |---------|---------|-----------|---------------------------------------|
 266:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****     |    1    |    0    |    1      |    | SB | 6 bit data | PB | STB |     |
 267:Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_usart.c ****     +-----------------------------------------------------------------------+
